Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本那么温柔 那么强大的人却…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是那样 其实他很软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…没能保护好他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为自己能让他从这个世界逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 他杀了许多自己人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他很弱?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 只能沉默不语 或随之疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 为什么都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做这种事情我也不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想让丸太你来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快闪开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 这种程度白是不会痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么弱 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋丸太 快闪开吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样 看着朋友被红衣男杀掉 渣到根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 「没有时间去考虑复仇」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你对我说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是「只要还有希望」 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子…我的光芒 已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有黑暗 和憎恨!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的痛苦 其实我无法体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是死了的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀掉的家伙再也回不来了 这种悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞和懊悔 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 凪的周围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全是光芒在闪耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你一直都低着头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连这种事都搞不清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪的身边不是有很多光芒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 光芒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的希望已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光 至今还在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 虽然做了很多过分的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我很弱 即使这是个疯狂的地方 也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 会保护我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫血? ?不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了 身体…麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 最后一次吃「Candy」是什么时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我挺起腰杆啊 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表我也有着重要的伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 唐子 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要哭要赎罪 等逃出这里后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泡我的修罗 你这混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大呼小叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难得让她得到了救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个想要见见自己孩子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个一心想要帮助别人的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜 生 艹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起作用?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧 想我救你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我避开了心脏和肺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该刺进骨头里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由你来把她送上西天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是她最好的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是憎恨一切 用杀戮来救赎的修罗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是个软弱的人类罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 怎会是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的救赎 就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 为了自由而并肩作战的同伴就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吧 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯掉的你很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀戮的身影也很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾爱着你呦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要变回那个无法普度众生的混帐伪君子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我来将你救赎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊 弦角…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布施的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又到镇上和人打架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为你是个温驯稳重的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶因只会招致恶果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不恨他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个扭曲的现世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦弱地不幸地 陷于无上的愚蠢之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普度众生的方法是否存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟真的就能逃脱生老病死么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么佛祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不知道什么是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却认定死亡是痛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 救救 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,益信 午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白 如何普度众生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静寂就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安宁即是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执枉也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善美都是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻悟也是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡才是救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吉 晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是挣扎着想逃出去的「Deadman」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能望着外界死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好的坟墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素蔓延 很痛苦吧 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地下就是你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恐惧中 僵化狂暴地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身沾满了着罪和五脏六腑而死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才能得到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我这个超级和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.51,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(729,653)}Grateful Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来赐予你们拯救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚空一闪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:53.70,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,653)}Invisible Black
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度就裂开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 他们必须被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 必须要哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我 什么都做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快挂掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜小猫还是做掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到被救赎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会一直拯救下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧 压抑 背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望 侮辱 后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂 痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会从fucking的世界中拯救你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫的 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 轮到我当Ace Man了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的大家都懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要有朋友在 就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁有闲工夫找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的救赎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十岚 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎 已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然充满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖的雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会出现美丽的彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 你不出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过很想出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能丢下朋友不管的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 之前打了你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我 还做了过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 已经不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还一起看到了闪闪轮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后有机会一起坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 还有哪里痛么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是糖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这件事以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角他们居然这么不顶用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色很不好啊 创办人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被死囚逃狱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 莳名小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的管辖区内没有少哪一个囚犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是还不习惯当所长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没经过交接 他突然就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我的管辖区内没有少人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5580号五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和9061号鹰见羊都回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这11天里 他们去了哪里 干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去审问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情况也许会上点家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没你的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.07,0:22:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会听到趣事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揉肩膀么 莳名长官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人选定好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从创始人名簿上的一般犯人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出了一名最合适人选
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有那么强的「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么味道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做尽坏事的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在不停地啄 森林已是千疮百孔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发怒了的森林之神 将它的喙变成了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦恼的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巢穴染上了毒 食物也染上了毒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友碰到它 全都相继地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的啄木鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩有毒的泪水闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是丸太的妈妈写的歌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很怀念 但还是别唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…红衣男也唱了这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个家伙 为什么会知道这首歌呢
